attributes.name: Hybrid Caramel Chews | 100mg
attributes.body:
A balanced blend. Buttery smooth, low calorie, creamy caramel with 10mg of fast acting THC in each bite sized chew. 100mg of high grade THC in each package.

Each batch of high grade cannabis oil used to make Cheeba Chews is tested at three critical stagesThe Flower, The Oil, The Edibleto ensure each individual chew is consistently infused.

Gluten, Peanut Free.

attributes.name: Indica Chocolate Taffy Chews | 100mg
attributes.body:
"Indica chews and chill" is the ideal way to describe the effects of these deliciously rich chocolate taffy chews. Each low calorie piece contains 10mg of THC, with ten chews in each package.

Known to provide a relaxing "body buzz", an indica chew is great to consume when you would like to unwind and decompress.

Each batch of high grade cannabis oil used to make Cheeba Chews is tested at three critical stagesThe Flower, The Oil, The Edibleto ensure each individual chew is consistently infused.

Gluten, Peanut Free.

KulluKush 1 Gram Tank - Pineapple Express
attributes.body:
Introducing the Kullukush 1 gram Tank in the Pineapple Express strain from Multitude Manufacturing. This tank is filled with a premium filtered distillate with over 90 percent THC potency and infused with a custom blend of live and botanical terpenes. KulluKush tanks are designed to provide you with a convenient and enjoyable cannabis experience. It's the pinnacle of potency and quality with the Kullukush Tank in the high-end I-Krusher ceramic reservoir.

Known for its focus, energizing, and euphoric effects, this tank offers a delightful combination of citrus, pine, and sweet flavors. With each puff, you'll experience a smooth and flavorful vapor that captures the essence of this popular strain.
